      "date": "2011-07-21 01:25:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nCould you please rebase on current master and re-submit?  I noticed that the EL5 build failed because it was trying to pull a very old kernel, indicating that the changeset is based on an old version of master.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 5
